Justice Ijeoma Ojukwu has varied Omoyele Sowore and Olawale Bakare's bail conditions. Justice Ojukwu said she found it difficult to believe a man of Sowore's pedigree did not have anyone to deposit N50 million. Sowore: From N100 million to N50 million and removes 50 million security deposits. Bakare: From N50 million to N20 million The case was adjourned until November 6 and 7